title: "Let's Start Arming Our Bunnies"
description: After spotting an angel though the glass, Dan & Jay send Jacob on a mission to find out her identity. The gang watches an Easter Bunny jump in on a fight & DJ Lou is guilted for choosing a date over friendship.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
